29:08.012 --> 29:09.514
- This last summer.

29:11.015 --> 29:12.917
- The Engagement party.

29:14.251 --> 29:15.586
You son of a bitch.

29:15.619 --> 29:16.587
- I didn't.
- You son of a bitch.

29:16.620 --> 29:17.488
- I didn't plan it, okay.

29:17.521 --> 29:19.257
