35:05.335 --> 35:06.437
- Gosh, what?

35:07.604 --> 35:09.573
- It's something you love.

35:09.606 --> 35:10.475
- What?

35:11.575 --> 35:13.177
- Finish your tea.

35:14.878 --> 35:16.580
