35:16.613 --> 35:18.716
(birds chirping)

35:18.749 --> 35:19.583
- Tell me.

35:19.617 --> 35:22.353
- Finish your tea, I'll finish
mine.

35:22.386 --> 35:25.256
(birds chirping)

35:30.360 --> 35:32.296
