35:44.675 --> 35:46.510
- You love acid?

35:46.543 --> 35:48.212
- That's not the point, Mark.

35:48.245 --> 35:49.547
What do you mean?

35:49.580 --> 35:50.681
- Okay, look, you're gonna have
to relax

35:50.714 --> 35:51.515
if you wanna have a good time.

35:51.548 --> 35:52.816
- Are you actually serious right
now?

35:52.849 --> 35:55.252
- For the next 10 to 12 hours.

35:55.285 --> 35:57.621
- You are absolutely
unbelievable.

35:57.654 --> 35:58.523
- Betty.

36:03.594 --> 36:04.462
- Fuck.

36:05.929 --> 36:07.965
