41:46.703 --> 41:47.337
Holy shit.

41:47.370 --> 41:50.040
(gentle music)

42:00.884 --> 42:03.153
(Betty laughing)

42:03.186 --> 42:04.021
- Oh God.

42:04.054 --> 42:06.757
(gentle music)

42:09.693 --> 42:10.561
- Wake up.

42:12.195 --> 42:13.130
- Don't joke.

42:13.163 --> 42:15.265
You know what was the best day
of my life.

42:15.298 --> 42:16.567
- It's the day you met me.

42:16.600 --> 42:17.868
- No.

42:17.901 --> 42:20.137
Unfortunately for your ego,

42:21.404 --> 42:23.173
I was about 12 or 13.

42:24.708 --> 42:26.777
Do you remember those, do
you remember these comments?

42:26.810 --> 42:29.813
The, the, the chain mail or
MySpace?

42:30.814 --> 42:32.349
- Look, I remember MySpace.

42:32.382 --> 42:33.283
I don't remember Yala.

42:33.316 --> 42:34.751
- Yeah.

42:34.784 --> 42:38.221
So it was one of those, you
know.

42:38.254 --> 42:39.790
I think it was like,

42:39.823 --> 42:41.325
"If you pass this on in 10 days,

42:41.358 --> 42:44.227
"then in a week, you'll have
the best day of your life

42:44.260 --> 42:46.196
"and in two weeks you'll
meet the love of your life."

42:46.229 --> 42:47.130
Or something like that.

42:47.164 --> 42:49.199
- Yeah, yeah and if you don't,
you'll die

42:49.232 --> 42:50.767
or the chick from the ring will
get you.

42:50.800 --> 42:51.635
- Yeah.

42:51.668 --> 42:52.336
(both laughing)

42:52.369 --> 42:54.671
- So I passed on one of those.

42:54.704 --> 42:56.640
- Oh, you are what's
wrong with this world.

42:56.673 --> 42:57.942
- Shut up, Mark.

42:59.743 --> 43:00.911
I passed on one of those

43:00.944 --> 43:05.749
and the next week I actually
had the best day of my life.

43:05.782 --> 43:08.051
I don't know, nothing happened
or changed

43:08.084 --> 43:10.721
because of the chain mail, but,

43:11.855 --> 43:14.925
I don't know, I just took
everything in.

43:14.958 --> 43:16.893
I'd never been so present.

43:16.926 --> 43:18.428
(birds chirping)

43:18.461 --> 43:23.767
Things I'd done a million times
suddenly became wonderful.

43:23.800 --> 43:26.436
I don't know, it's hard to
explain.

43:26.469 --> 43:28.372
It wasn't even sunny.

43:28.405 --> 43:31.642
It was raining, but it was
beautiful.

43:33.276 --> 43:34.645
- No, I get it.

43:36.379 --> 43:39.316
Have you had a day like that
since?

43:40.216 --> 43:41.285
- I think so.

43:43.386 --> 43:45.823
Nowhere as good, but I have.

43:47.857 --> 43:51.428
I think it happens when
I have a recurrence.

43:53.763 --> 43:55.032
I think I'm feeling it.

43:55.065 --> 43:57.835
(both laughing)

43:59.836 --> 44:00.871
- Yeah.

44:00.904 --> 44:04.441
I swear I only feel that way on
drugs.

44:04.474 --> 44:05.976
Well, some drugs.

44:07.444 --> 44:10.247
Most kinda just push you away
from it,

44:10.280 --> 44:12.282
from the present.

44:12.315 --> 44:15.085
Now that's the problem.

44:15.118 --> 44:17.021
It's not being present.

44:18.121 --> 44:20.257
I was a bit of a depressed kid.

44:20.290 --> 44:22.893
I think I watched too much TV.

44:23.793 --> 44:27.431
I just, I always wanted
to be somewhere else,

44:28.531 --> 44:30.300
somewhere green.

44:30.333 --> 44:31.368
- Hmm.

44:31.401 --> 44:35.005
- You know, in some
fantasy world full of magic

44:35.038 --> 44:38.308
where I was the chosen
one in a great story.

44:38.341 --> 44:40.778
You know, and I had friends.

44:43.847 --> 44:47.184
God, I was always in my head,
you know,

44:47.217 --> 44:49.486
and I, I never looked around

44:49.519 --> 44:52.322
'cause it just made me sad

44:52.355 --> 44:56.259
'cause it wasn't where I wanted
to be.

44:56.292 --> 45:00.263
Yeah, there's nothing
fantastical about the suburbs.

45:00.296 --> 45:02.900
So I would live in a daydream.

45:05.535 --> 45:08.839
And that way of thinking, you
know, at least for so long,

45:08.872 --> 45:12.009
I think it built pathways in my
brain.

45:13.510 --> 45:16.880
I can't be present and it kills
me.

45:16.913 --> 45:18.982
(gentle music)

45:19.015 --> 45:20.851
It's like I'm drifting.

45:20.884 --> 45:22.219
(gentle music)

45:22.252 --> 45:26.123
Holding my breath as the
waves crash above me.

45:28.224 --> 45:31.795
I wanted that feeling
that you're talking about,

45:31.828 --> 45:32.896
so damn much.

45:34.831 --> 45:38.435
And this weekend I'm starting to
feel it.

45:38.468 --> 45:40.270
(gentle music)

45:40.303 --> 45:42.572
It's like what you said,

45:42.605 --> 45:45.175
it happens after a recurrence.

45:45.208 --> 45:47.477
(gentle music)

45:47.510 --> 45:50.380
It's when you've accepted it,
